msgstr "स्थाने स्थातुं सूचयति कर्सरः ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Custom Themes"
msgstr "कस्टम् थीम्स् संस्थापनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order for &killbots; to detect and use a new theme, the files must be "
"moved to an appropriate directory. To install the theme for only the current "
"user, copy the desktop, preview and &SVG; files to <filename class="
"\"directory\">killbots/themes</filename> in the local folder in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation </"
"option></userinput>. To make the theme available system wide, move the files "
"to <filename class=\"directory\">killbots/themes</filename> in the system "
"folder (from the previous command, possibly <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"usr/share</filename> or similar). Note that this will likely require "
"administrative privileges."
msgstr ""
"क्रमेण &amp;killbots; नूतनं विषयं ज्ञातुं उपयोक्तुं च सञ्चिकाः समुचितनिर्देशिकायां "
"स्थानान्तरितव्याः । केवलं वर्तमानस्य उपयोक्तुः कृते विषयवस्तुं संस्थापयितुं, डेस्कटॉप्, पूर्वावलोकनं "
"तथा &amp;SVG; सञ्चिकाः to<filename class=\"directory\"> killbots/विषयाणि</"
"filename> स्थानीयपुटे in<userinput><command> qtpaths इति</command><option value="
"\"--paths GenericDataLocation\"> --paths सामान्यदत्तांशस्थान</option></"
"userinput> . विषयं प्रणाली विस्तृतं उपलब्धं कर्तुं सञ्चिकाः अत्र स्थानान्तरयन्तु<filename "
"class=\"directory\"> killbots/विषयाणि</filename> सिस्टम् समुच्चय मध्ये (पूर्वादेशात्, "
"सम्भवतः<filename class=\"directory\"> /usr/share इति</filename> तत्सदृशं वा) । "
"ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् एतदर्थं सम्भवतः प्रशासनिकविशेषाधिकारस्य आवश्यकता भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating Custom Game Types"
msgstr "कस्टम् गेम टाइप्स् इत्यस्य निर्माणम्"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Ruleset Desktop File"
msgstr "नियमसमूहः डेस्कटॉप् सञ्चिका"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating new game types is incredibly simple for &killbots;, especially when "
"starting from an existing ruleset file. Rulesets are stored as a single "
"desktop file where the parameters and metadata are stored as simple key-"
"value pairs."
msgstr ""
"नूतनक्रीडाप्रकारस्य निर्माणं &killbots;, कृते अविश्वसनीयतया सरलं भवति, विशेषतः यदा "
"विद्यमाननियमसमूहसञ्चिकातः आरभ्यते । नियमसमूहाः एकस्याः डेस्कटॉप् सञ्चिकारूपेण संगृह्यन्ते यत्र "
"पैरामीटर्स् मेटाडाटा च सरलकुंजी-मूल्ययुग्मरूपेण संगृहीताः भवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Default &killbots; Game Type"
msgstr "पूर्वनिर्धारितं &killbots; गेम प्रकार"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[KillbotsRuleset]\n"
"Name=Killbots\n"
"Name[gl]=Robots asasinos\n"
"Author=Parker Coates\n"
"AuthorContact=parker.coates@kdemail.net\n"
"Description=&lt;qt&gt;&lt;p&gt;The default Killbots game type.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;"
"p&gt;Includes a medium size grid, safe teleports, fast enemies and pushable "
"junkheaps.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/qt&gt;\n"
"Description[gl]=&lt;qt&gt;&lt;p&gt;O xogo tipo Killbots por omisión.&lt;/"
"p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Inclúe unha grella mediana, teleportacións seguras, enemigos "
"rápidos e chatarra que se pode empurrar.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/qt&gt;\n"
"Rows=16\n"
"Columns=16\n"
"EnemiesAtGameStart=8.0\n"
"EnemiesAddedEachRound=4.0\n"
"FastEnemiesAtGameStart=-2.0\n"
"FastEnemiesAddedEachRound=2.0\n"
"EnergyEnabled=true\n"
"EnergyAtGameStart=0\n"
"EnergyAddedEachRound=0\n"
"MaxEnergyAtGameStart=12.0\n"
"MaxEnergyAddedEachRound=0.0\n"
"SafeTeleportEnabled=true\n"
"CostOfSafeTeleport=1\n"
"VaporizerEnabled=false\n"
"CostOfVaporizer=0\n"
"PushableJunkheaps=Many\n"
"SquaskKillsEnabled=true\n"
"JunkheapsAtGameStart=0.0\n"
"JunkheapsAddedEachRound=0.0\n"
"PointsPerEnemyKilled=5\n"
"PointsPerFastEnemyKilled=10\n"
"WaitKillPointBonus=0\n"
"WaitKillEnergyBonus=1\n"
"SquashKillPointBonus=0\n"
"SquashKillEnergyBonus=1"
msgstr ""
"[KillbotsRuleset] इति ।\n"
"नाम=किल्बोट्स\n"
"नाम[gl]=रोबोट् अस्सिनो\n"
"लेखक=पार्कर कोट्स\n"
"लेखकसंपर्क=parker.coates@kdemail.net\n"
"विवरण=&lt;qt&gt;&lt;p&gt;पूर्वनिर्धारितः Killbots क्रीडाप्रकारः।&lt;/p&gt;&lt;"
"p&gt;मध्यम आकारस्य जालम्, सुरक्षितं टेलीपोर्ट्स्, द्रुतशत्रवः, धक्कायमानाः जङ्कीप्स् च "
"समाविष्टाः सन्ति।&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/qt&gt;\n"
"विवरण[gl]=&lt;qt&gt;&lt;p&gt;ओ xogo tipo Killbots por omisión।&lt;/p&gt;&lt;"
"p&gt;Inclúe unha grella mediana, teleportaciones seguras, enemigos rápidos ई "
"चतर्रा क्वे से पोडे एम्पुररर।&lt;/p&gt ;&lt;/qt&gt;\n"
"पङ्क्तयः=१६\n"
"स्तम्भ=16\n"
"EnemiesAtGameStart = 8.0\n"
"शत्रुजोडितप्रत्येकगोल=4.0\n"
"FastEnemiesAtGameStart=-2.0\n"
"द्रुतशत्रुजोडित प्रत्येक गोल = 2.0\n"
"ऊर्जासक्षमम्=सत्यम्\n"
"ऊर्जाAtGameStart=0\n"
"ऊर्जाजोडित प्रत्येक गोल = 0\n"
"अधिकतम ऊर्जाAtGameStart = 12.0\n"
"अधिकतम ऊर्जाAddedEachRound = 0.0\n"
"SafeTeleportEnabled=सत्यम्\n"
"CostOfSafeTeleport=1\n"
"वाष्पीकरणसक्षमम्=मिथ्या\n"
"CostOfVaporizer=0\n"
"PushableJunkheaps=बहु\n"
"SquaskKillsEnabled=सत्यम्\n"
"JunkheapsAtGameStart = 0.0\n"
"JunkheapsAddedEachRound = 0.0\n"
"PointsPerEnemyKilled = 5\n"
"PointsPerFastEnemyKilled = 10\n"
"प्रतीक्षा मारबिन्दुबोनस = 0\n"
"प्रतीक्षा मार ऊर्जाबोनस = 1\n"
"स्क्वैशकिलपॉइंटबोनस = 0\n"
"स्क्वैशकिलएनर्जीबोनस=1"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that all text parameters should be entered in American English. As seen "
"in the example above, translations can be added to the desktop file by "
"repeating the key and appending the language code between square brackets. "
"Also note that rich text can be given to the <varname>Description</varname> "
"field by wrapping the value in &lt;qt&gt; tags."
msgstr ""
"ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् सर्वे पाठमापदण्डाः अमेरिकन-आङ्ग्लभाषायां प्रविष्टव्याः । यथा उपरि उदाहरणे "
"दृश्यते, कीलस्य पुनरावृत्तिः कृत्वा वर्गकोष्ठकानां मध्ये भाषासङ्केतं योजयित्वा डेस्कटॉप् सञ्चिकायां "
"अनुवादाः योजयितुं शक्यन्ते । इदमपि ज्ञातव्यं यत् <varname>Description</varname> क्षेत्रे "
"मूल्यं &lt;qt&gt; टैग्स।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "A ruleset file should contain all of the following parameters."
msgstr "नियमसमूहसञ्चिकायां निम्नलिखितसर्वमापदण्डाः भवेयुः ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "नामः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the ruleset as it will appear in the ruleset selector and the "
"high score dialog."
msgstr "नियमसमूहस्य नाम यथा नियमसमूहचयनके उच्चाङ्कसंवादे च दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Author"
msgstr "लेखकः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "The creator of the ruleset."
msgstr "नियमसमूहस्य निर्माता ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "AuthorContact"
msgstr "लेखकसंपर्क"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contact information of the creator. This is usually an email address."
msgstr "रचनाकारस्य सम्पर्कसूचना। प्रायः एतत् ईमेल-सङ्केतं भवति ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A description of the ruleset. This should give a decent overview of the game "
"type, but it doesn't need to list the value of each parameter as this "
"information can been seen in the Details dialog."
msgstr ""
"नियमसमूहस्य वर्णनम् । एतेन क्रीडाप्रकारस्य सभ्यं अवलोकनं दातव्यं, परन्तु प्रत्येकस्य पैरामीटर् "
"इत्यस्य मूल्यं सूचीकरणस्य आवश्यकता नास्ति यतः एषा सूचना Details संवादे द्रष्टुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rows"
msgstr "पङ्क्तयः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of rows in the game grid."
msgstr "क्रीडाजालस्य पङ्क्तिसङ्ख्या ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Columns"
msgstr "स्तम्भाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of columns in the game grid."
msgstr "क्रीडाजालस्य स्तम्भानां संख्या ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "EnemiesAtGameStart"
msgstr "शत्रून्AtGameStart"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of regular enemies added to the grid at the start of the first "
"round."
msgstr "प्रथमपरिक्रमायाः आरम्भे नियमितशत्रुणां संख्या जालपुटे वर्धिता ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "EnemiesAddedEachRound"
msgstr "शत्रून्AddedEachRound इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of additional regular enemies added to the grid at the start of "
"each round."
msgstr "प्रत्येकस्य गोलस्य आरम्भे जालपुटे अतिरिक्तनियमितशत्रुणां संख्या वर्धिता ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "FastEnemiesAtGameStart"
msgstr "द्रुतशत्रवःखेलप्रारम्भे"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of fast enemies added to the grid at the start of the first round."
msgstr "प्रथमपरिक्रमायाः आरम्भे द्रुतशत्रुणां संख्या जालपुटे योजितवती ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "FastEnemiesAddedEachRound"
msgstr "FastEnemiesAddedEachRound इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of additional fast enemies added to the grid at the start of each "
"round."
msgstr "प्रत्येकस्य गोलस्य आरम्भे जालपुटे अतिरिक्तानां द्रुतशत्रुणां संख्या वर्धिता ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "EnergyEnabled"
msgstr "ऊर्जासक्षमम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to <quote><constant>false</constant></quote> the hero will be enable "
"to earn or spend energy."
msgstr ""
"यदि <quote><constant>false</constant></quote> इति सेट् भवति तर्हि नायकः ऊर्जां "
"अर्जयितुं वा व्ययितुं वा समर्थः भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "EnergyAtGameStart"
msgstr "ऊर्जाAtGameStart"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The amount of energy awarded to the hero at the start of the first round."
msgstr "प्रथमपरिक्रमायाः आरम्भे नायकाय यत् ऊर्जायाः परिमाणं प्रदत्तं तत् ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "EnergyAddedEachRound"
msgstr "ऊर्जाAddedEachRound"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of energy awarded to the hero at the start of each round."
msgstr "प्रत्येकस्य चक्रस्य आरम्भे नायकाय प्रदत्तस्य ऊर्जायाः परिमाणम् ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "MaxEnergyAtGameStart"
msgstr "MaxEnergyAtGameStart इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The maximum energy capacity of the hero at the start of the first round."
msgstr "प्रथमपरिक्रमस्य आरम्भे नायकस्य अधिकतमं ऊर्जाक्षमता।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "MaxEnergyAddedEachRound"
msgstr "MaxEnergyAddedEachRound इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "The change in maximum energy capacity at the start of each round."
msgstr "प्रत्येकस्य चक्रस्य आरम्भे अधिकतम ऊर्जाक्षमतायाः परिवर्तनम् ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "SafeTeleportEnabled"
msgstr "सुरक्षितदूरवाहनसक्षमम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to <quote><constant>false</constant></quote> the safe teleport action "
"will be disabled."
msgstr ""
"यदि <quote><constant>false</constant></quote> इति सेट् भवति तर्हि सुरक्षितं "
"दूरस्थापनक्रिया निष्क्रियं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "CostOfSafeTeleport"
msgstr "CostOfSafeTeleport इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of energy consumed by teleporting safely."
msgstr "सुरक्षितरूपेण दूरस्थापनेन यत् ऊर्जायाः उपभोगः भवति ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "VaporizerEnabled"
msgstr "वाष्पीकरणसक्षमम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to <quote><constant>false</constant></quote> the vaporizer action "
"will be disabled."
msgstr ""
"यदि <quote><constant>false</constant></quote> इति सेट् भवति तर्हि वाष्पीकरणक्रिया "
"निष्क्रियं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "CostOfVaporizer"
msgstr "CostOfVaporizer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of energy consumed by using the vaporizer."
msgstr "वाष्पीकरणकस्य उपयोगेन यत् ऊर्जायाः उपभोगः भवति ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "PushableJunkheaps"
msgstr "धक्कायोग्यजंखेप्स्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of junkheaps that can be moved with a single push. Possible "
"values are <quote><constant>None</constant></quote>, <quote><constant>One</"
"constant></quote> and <quote><constant>Many</constant></quote>."
msgstr ""
"एकेन धक्कानेन चालयितुं शक्यमाणानां जङ्कीपानां संख्या। सम्भाव्यमूल्यानि <quote><constant>न "
"कश्चित्</constant></quote>, <quote><constant>एकः</constant></quote> "
"<quote><constant>बहु</constant></quote> च सन्ति ."

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "SquaskKillsEnabled"
msgstr "SquaskKillsEnabled इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "If true, the hero can squash enemies by pushing junkheaps onto them."
msgstr "यदि सत्यं तर्हि नायकः शत्रून् उपरि जङ्कीप्स् धक्कायन् स्क्वैश कर्तुं शक्नोति।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "JunkheapsAtGameStart"
msgstr "JunkheapsAtGameप्रारम्भ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of junkheaps placed on the grid at the start of the first round."
msgstr "प्रथमपरिक्रमायाः आरम्भे जालपुटे स्थापितानां जङ्कीपानां संख्या।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "JunkheapsAddedEachRound"
msgstr "JunkheapsAddedप्रत्येकगोल"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of additional junkheaps placed on the grid at the start of each "
"round."
msgstr "प्रत्येकस्य गोलस्य आरम्भे जालपुटे स्थापितानां अतिरिक्तजङ्कीपानां संख्या।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "PointsPerEnemyKilled"
msgstr "PointsPerEnemy मारित"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of points awarded for destroying a regular enemy."
msgstr "नियमितशत्रुनाशार्थं प्रदत्तानां अंकानाम् संख्या ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "PointsPerFastEnemyKilled"
msgstr "PointsPerFastEnemyहत्या हुआ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of points awarded for destroying a fast enemy."
msgstr "द्रुतशत्रुनाशार्थं प्रदत्तानां अंकानाम् संख्या ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "WaitKillPointBonus"
msgstr "प्रतीक्षा किलपॉइंटबोनस"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of bonus points awarded for destroying an enemy while waiting out "
"the round."
msgstr "गोलस्य बहिः प्रतीक्षमाणस्य शत्रुस्य नाशस्य कृते प्रदत्तानां बोनस-बिन्दुनां संख्या ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid "WaitKillEnergyBonus"
msgstr "WaitKillEnergyBonus इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of bonus energy units awarded for destroying an enemy while "
"waiting out the round."
msgstr "गोलस्य बहिः प्रतीक्षमाणस्य शत्रुस्य नाशार्थं प्रदत्तानां बोनस ऊर्जा-एककानां संख्या ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "SquashKillPointBonus"
msgstr "स्क्वैशकिलपॉइंटबोनस"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of bonus points awarded for squashing an enemy with a junkheap."
msgstr "शत्रुं जङ्कीप् इत्यनेन स्क्वैश कृत्वा प्रदत्तानां बोनस्-बिन्दुनां संख्या ।"

#. Tag: varname
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "SquashKillEnergyBonus"
msgstr "स्क्वैशकिल्लऊर्जाबोनस"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of bonus energy units awarded for squashing an enemy with a "
"junkheap."
msgstr "शत्रुं जङ्कीपेन कूर्दितुं प्रदत्तानां बोनस ऊर्जा-एककानां संख्या ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Custom Game Types"
msgstr "कस्टम् गेम टाइप्स् संस्थापनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order for &killbots; to detect and use a new game type, the ruleset file "
"must be moved to an appropriate directory. To install the game type for only "
"the current user, copy the file to <filename class=\"directory\">killbots/"
"rulesets</filename> in the local folder in <userinput><command>qtpaths</"
"command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation </option></userinput>. To make "
"the game type available system wide, move the file to <filename class="
"\"directory\">killbots/rulesets</filename> in the system folder (from the "
"previous command, possibly <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/share</"
"filename> or similar). Note that this will likely require administrative "
"privileges."
msgstr ""
"क्रमेण &amp;killbots; नूतनं क्रीडाप्रकारस्य अन्वेषणाय उपयोगाय च नियमसमूहसञ्चिकां "
"समुचितनिर्देशिकायां स्थानान्तरितव्या । केवलं वर्तमानप्रयोक्तुः कृते क्रीडाप्रकारं संस्थापयितुं, "
"सञ्चिकां प्रतिलिख्यताम्<filename class=\"directory\"> killbots/नियमसमूहाः</"
"filename> स्थानीयपुटे in<userinput><command> qtpaths इति</command><option value="
"\"--paths GenericDataLocation\"> --paths सामान्यदत्तांशस्थान</option></"
"userinput> . क्रीडाप्रकारं प्रणालीव्यापीं उपलब्धं कर्तुं सञ्चिकां स्थापयन्तु<filename class="
"\"directory\"> killbots/नियमसमूहाः</filename> सिस्टम् समुच्चय मध्ये (पूर्वादेशात्, "
"सम्भवतः<filename class=\"directory\"> /usr/share इति</filename> तत्सदृशं वा) । "
"ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् एतदर्थं सम्भवतः प्रशासनिकविशेषाधिकारस्य आवश्यकता भविष्यति ।"

